{"tid":1468400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乖啦大家！！！大家放低電話停一停 諗一諗","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T07:39:16.000Z","uid":135845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c50ff90a582605c18880ab7fe40ef6fdc421829e","tid":1468400,"uid":135845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:41.000Z","msg":"每次行動之後永遠都有兩批人互相指責 覺得對方做嘅嘢唔啱 每次後續都係互屌 但係大家仲記唔記得<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋嘅目的係咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n我知大家好嬲 有好多唔同意見 <br />\n但係希望大家勿忘初衷 <br />\n我哋一樣訴求都未達成 互相指責對件事無幫助<br />\n<br />\n我知現今社會大家都習慣咗依賴社交網絡 但係對家可能就係正正捉住依點去分化我哋 依家消息流通 不論係假消息定係分化post都好快滲入 容易被帶風向 <br />\n<br />\n我希望大家只要記住我哋目的係咩？身邊手足嘅目的係咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方法不一 目的一樣 不分化 不割席啊大家</span>"},{"pid":"aa7ed179c659b13529a29249d767372c8ecd0709","tid":1468400,"uid":135845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">核彈都唔割啊！！！！！！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"1aef61b2626aef182f30f35a61754d7e4491ed1d","tid":1468400,"uid":135845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5268da0f48820a446780f6269d3aa02d0618147e","tid":1468400,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:56.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！永不放棄！"},{"pid":"e290244cdc9de836b14e67f2d69213b9ae888f67","tid":1468400,"uid":135845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5268da0f48820a446780f6269d3aa02d0618147e","tid":1468400,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:56.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！永不放棄！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmo